webrss new generation:
=====================

0. Start-up

   tclsh rss-nt.sh

   + automatically logs to /tmp/rssnt.log
   
   

1. Allow parallel downloading
   + more responsive updates
   + one site doesn't need to wait for other sites
   + timeouts







===============================================================================
youtube-podcast:
===============

cd ~/youtube/asakawaz
update doit.tcl for latest contents
tclsh doit.tcl
tclsh ~/tomei/web2rss/youtube_podcasts/organize.tcl

http://localhost:9015/podcasts/asakawaz/podcast.xml


